{"tid":457430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廣東話拉丁化討論","createTime":"2017-11-04T00:45:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T01:07:13.000Z","uid":144372,"like":8,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"f99339411fd8643f821f766d5e211da2b4f0ec42","tid":457430,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T00:45:11.000Z","msg":"中原語言解會比人同化，其中一個原因係用中文字，現代中文就係基於北方語文諗嘢，要真正有自己系統同方便鬼佬學，應該拉丁化，而家開始呢個post全面改用粵拼打字<br />\n<br />\n我一早預咗有人入嚟屌，歡迎，但係我教過鬼佬廣東話，佢哋打字都淨係打粵拼<br />\n<br />\nZou2 san4, gam3 do1 wai2, sik6 zo2 zou2 caan1 mei6"},{"pid":"a69bdc84d81094a18cac076f9bdb412f8f0dff1f","tid":457430,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T00:48:10.000Z","msg":"Hou2 do1 lin4 dang1 zai2 gong2 zau6 waa6 gwok3 zai3 faa3, jau6 waa6 jit6 oi3 gwong2 dung1 waa2<br />\n<br />\nJyu4 gwok3 zing6 hai6 jung4 zhong1 man1 zi6, gwai2 lou2 dim2 hok6?<br />\n<br />\nNei5 tai2 jyut6 naam4 waa2, zung6 jung2 gan2 hon3 zi6 go2 si4, lin4 jyut6 naam4 jan4 zi6 gei2 dou1 m4 ming4"},{"pid":"ed60d710bf2db1bcf327e706d27c16b3269852bb","tid":457430,"uid":5921,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T00:49:44.000Z","msg":"upmud9"},{"pid":"0cb8dc7c5d8d2a14b28c28c945366fb30d94c586","tid":457430,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T00:50:25.000Z","msg":"O5 m4 zi1 jung6 ni1 tou3 ping3 jam1 hou2 m4 hou2, daan6 hai6 nei5 zung2 jiu3 jau5 go3 fong1 faat3 bei2 jan4 hok6 gwaa2?<br />\n<br />\nM4 tung1 giu3 go3 aam1 aam1 lai4 hoeng1 gong2 ge3 jan4 zau6 gam2 deoi3 zyu1 zung1 man2 duk6?"},{"pid":"cce0b2c04771297b67478e49dc5bfea8e2da7a96","tid":457430,"uid":128748,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T00:51:07.000Z","msg":"為咗方便鬼佬學習而放棄自己民族語言特性"},{"pid":"6800639f9cbcdb7097f435cecf8fd17adb0cdd8e","tid":457430,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T00:52:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>upmud9</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nNei5 m4 ming4 nei5 ge3 si6, lin4 zi6 gei2 jyu5 jin4 oi6 gwok3 jan4 dim2 hok6 dou1 m4 zi1<br />\n<br />\nZung6 hai2 dou6 man6 jan4 ap1 mat1 ceon1<br />\n<br />\nZi6 m4 zi1 cau2"},{"pid":"d1af50e0ab475f1ad5eb8f64a0dda1830a741444","tid":457430,"uid":398,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T00:52:26.000Z","msg":"做乜撚野。。"},{"pid":"6e17d882d4b565b55165de1e3fd280daacce70fb","tid":457430,"uid":11793,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T00:53:07.000Z","msg":"Onlun99"},{"pid":"75d377d6bd7784b8cbb4039fdbf079424f029f9a","tid":457430,"uid":7529,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T00:53:36.000Z","msg":"支持粵拼令學習同標音系統化，書寫都係用返漢字好"},{"pid":"cbe16529fb74c08a83fe7ba9321c4eb593a6b93a","tid":457430,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T00:53:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>為咗方便鬼佬學習而放棄自己民族語言特性</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nNei5 go3 man4 zuk6 hai6 me1<br />\n<br />\nGwong2 dung1 waa2 m4 jing1  goi1 ji1 fu6 hai2 zung1 man2 dou6"},{"pid":"cf3791421902b84b58e1a0da67cd7a695f14eef7","tid":457430,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T00:54:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支持粵拼令學習同標音系統化，書寫都係用返漢字好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nJyu4 gwok2 jau5 gwai2 lou2 gam2 daa2, nei5 jau6 diu2 jan4?"},{"pid":"3b85be04ee67aaf0453f6a2a3fb8ab1e0cc17436","tid":457430,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T00:56:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Onlun99</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nJat1 hoi1 ci5 oi6 gwok3 cyun4 gaau3 si6 faat3 ming4 jyut6 ping1<br />\n<br />\nZau6 hai6 zi1 tung4 bak1 fong1 gun1 fong1 zung1 man2 caa1 taai3 jyun5<br />\n<br />\nZung1 man2 biu1 daat6 m4 dou2"},{"pid":"80bcadb64b9e9d35ee9126d02adc6a0c5528d232","tid":457430,"uid":68802,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T00:56:10.000Z","msg":"Sor我覺得香港同台灣叫做真正正統中華文化嘅繼承<br />\n支那唔係<br />\n我地應該做嘅應該係將佢本土化而唔係將佢拉丁化<br />\n見到好多拉丁化/拼音化嘅最終只係將外來語音譯<br />\n咁不如直接講英文啦屌"},{"pid":"50f474c12355bea3d25f3bd4f898166070e13cba","tid":457430,"uid":84772,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T00:56:23.000Z","msg":"搞咩搞返新文化運動入面最柒嗰樣嘢出嚟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中文字太多同音字所以冇咩可能做到，<br />\n同埋本身中文已經好難描述一個字嘅讀法，<br />\n更何況廣東話比普通話複雜咁多。"},{"pid":"0a217f721041043841c344212ea1084c85822443","tid":457430,"uid":21664,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T00:58:00.000Z","msg":"好似傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"660f3f0c7ba7b284adc3096214d506a82f0ee78d","tid":457430,"uid":7529,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T00:58:34.000Z","msg":"一個音節通常對應幾個漢字，所謂拉丁化書寫只表讀音，讀者要根據context搵返對應既漢字理解，咁點解一開始唔用漢字要做多個步驟多鳩餘呢？"},{"pid":"aa0c244ea9628004c6bed7fa45b4d137431ad8e6","tid":457430,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T00:58:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Sor我覺得香港同台灣叫做真正正統中華文化嘅繼承<br />\n支那唔係<br />\n我地應該做嘅應該係將佢本土化而唔係將佢拉丁化<br />\n見到好多拉丁化/拼音化嘅最終只係將外來語音譯<br />\n咁不如直接講英文啦屌</blockquote><br />\n <br />\nO5 hai6 hoeng1 gong2 jan4<br />\nJau5 me1 zaak3 jam6 cyun4 sing4 zung1 waa3 man4 faa3?"},{"pid":"4dee167562415955f7ea9bbf4b218b5ce45eb45b","tid":457430,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T01:00:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一個音節通常對應幾個漢字，所謂拉丁化書寫只表讀音，讀者要根據context搵返對應既漢字理解，咁點解一開始唔用漢字要做多個步驟多鳩餘呢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nNei5 zan1 hai6 cyun4 bou6 zi6 sik1 daa2 gwong2 dung1 waa2?<br />\n<br />\nZau6) syun3 ni1 dou6 dou1 daai6 baa2 fo2 sing1 man6 tung1 jam1 zi6 daa2 ceot1 lai4"},{"pid":"ed8850d7b8e0b78b35071391bf842cc92b353a05","tid":457430,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T01:02:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nGam2 nei5 jau6 jap6 lai4?"},{"pid":"5a5b50f3a50b3927c2b87e4019b854a4b8dcd90a","tid":457430,"uid":109462,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T01:04:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一個音節通常對應幾個漢字，所謂拉丁化書寫只表讀音，讀者要根據context搵返對應既漢字理解，咁點解一開始唔用漢字要做多個步驟多鳩餘呢？</blockquote><br />\n同韓國佬用諺文搞到「防水」變「放水」一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3589f93403e54a373abc36154a74077b6b9ee46a","tid":457430,"uid":86841,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T01:04:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c8271380aaeed8c66d6022ccca7df8b53ad9c07b","tid":457430,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T01:05:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Sor我覺得香港同台灣叫做真正正統中華文化嘅繼承<br />\n支那唔係<br />\n我地應該做嘅應該係將佢本土化而唔係將佢拉丁化<br />\n見到好多拉丁化/拼音化嘅最終只係將外來語音譯<br />\n咁不如直接講英文啦屌</blockquote><br />\n支那係蘇維埃同馬克斯嘅繼續者,根本就係外來政權嚟<br />\n所以我支持繼續用番正體字,不過係粵語入文啫"},{"pid":"8d69d25f1e5d8c650c9f338b6edcf7dd0d058f94","tid":457430,"uid":68802,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T01:05:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一個音節通常對應幾個漢字，所謂拉丁化書寫只表讀音，讀者要根據context搵返對應既漢字理解，咁點解一開始唔用漢字要做多個步驟多鳩餘呢？</blockquote><br />\n就好似on9韓文咁撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當初要棄中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我地應該睇成正體中文係舊中原地區傳承俾港台兩地嘅文化根源<br />\n而中原已經係成為殘體支那文化<br />\n我地應該係對正體中文有絕對嘅決定權<br />\n唔再想同中華兩隻字有關 我地可以改為港台文化 或者正體中文文化<br />\n<br />\n拉丁化真係好撚on9就鬼佬架咋<br />\n鬼佬識得一種字 唔明咩叫象形文字架"},{"pid":"aaff17553bd1cca65b3670c212b2aac7bc9da27e","tid":457430,"uid":139349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T01:07:51.000Z","msg":"留名睇中華膠同番膠大戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcfc5b2a623810e4651583610a4c040020ff7c67","tid":457430,"uid":7529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T01:08:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一個音節通常對應幾個漢字，所謂拉丁化書寫只表讀音，讀者要根據context搵返對應既漢字理解，咁點解一開始唔用漢字要做多個步驟多鳩餘呢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nNei5 zan1 hai6 cyun4 bou6 zi6 sik1 daa2 gwong2 dung1 waa2?<br />\n<br />\nZau6) syun3 ni1 dou6 dou1 daai6 baa2 fo2 sing1 man6 tung1 jam1 zi6 daa2 ceot1 lai4</blockquote><br />\n有啲字「唔識」只係因為廣州話冇標準化/規範化，例如如果教育局規範「ge3」（用於連接名詞）做漢字「嘅」，香港人由小學就學呢個字，咁好多人都會「識」"},{"pid":"d7b9fe84e830be27c3ad78339322f3b5323caa72","tid":457430,"uid":68802,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T01:08:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Sor我覺得香港同台灣叫做真正正統中華文化嘅繼承<br />\n支那唔係<br />\n我地應該做嘅應該係將佢本土化而唔係將佢拉丁化<br />\n見到好多拉丁化/拼音化嘅最終只係將外來語音譯<br />\n咁不如直接講英文啦屌</blockquote><br />\n支那係蘇維埃同馬克斯嘅繼續者,根本就係外來政權嚟<br />\n所以我支持繼續用番正體字,不過係粵語入文啫</blockquote><br />\n無錯<br />\n正體中文已經由中原變到唔係中原<br />\n我地繼承左當然可以就返我地地域文化不同而作改變啦<br />\n依家中原嗰班支那人對我地正體中文跟本無資格指手劃腳"},{"pid":"cd7df1964895f9f5e814a78834815f980f552676","tid":457430,"uid":22858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T01:09:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>盲反中國無所不用其技<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">JR收皮仆街冚家鏟</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><ins>細字濃縮試用版</ins><br />\n經crosscheck多個post，確信五毛名單臚列如下：三色貓、法國佬巫斯義、群龍共舞、優美開始、JR、RedBaron、Gladiclus、D_Wade、dewi、newlife、bbchu、十卜Ching、侵B、吾系甘開心牙、返六日唔撚易、毛澤東<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji