g1 man6 tung1 jam1 zi6 daa2 ceot1 lai4</blockquote><br />\n有啲字「唔識」只係因為廣州話冇標準化/規範化，例如如果教育局規範「ge3」（用於連接名詞）做漢字「嘅」，香港人由小學就學呢個字，咁好多人都會「識」</blockquote><br />\n對於嘅/d依d字我覺得可以寬鬆處理<br />\n重點要入教育系統依家難道好高<br />\n由支共統治之下依d咁local嘅野佢應該唔會俾你入"},{"pid":"adff11354c13281cabc5b65b4fd0cdea077e86f2","tid":457430,"uid":47359,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T01:14:18.000Z","msg":"漢字係廣東話既神髓之一<br />\n<br />\n於雨餘，於汝寓，汝娛余，汝予乳，予余娛，余預羽，羽娛乳，娛乳餘，汝如雨，余御汝，如魚愉，御汝餘，愈譽余。"},{"pid":"88b3cdb3c7f33b9306a574f754e425c8e6d2b34e","tid":457430,"uid":139349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T01:15:02.000Z","msg":"各個國家有各個國家既國歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，呢句點變？"},{"pid":"4b5fa06b9ce3917e7470622d8466037ebdb1a6f3","tid":457430,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T01:15:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Sor我覺得香港同台灣叫做真正正統中華文化嘅繼承<br />\n支那唔係<br />\n我地應該做嘅應該係將佢本土化而唔係將佢拉丁化<br />\n見到好多拉丁化/拼音化嘅最終只係將外來語音譯<br />\n咁不如直接講英文啦</blockquote><br />\n中國文化是優美的，只是被共產黨破壞了！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/395280?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/395280?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"736a89ba8b87696300a953e8714b9098171bdfef","tid":457430,"uid":47359,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T01:15:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>漢字係廣東話既神髓之一<br />\n<br />\n於雨餘，於汝寓，汝娛余，汝予乳，予余娛，余預羽，羽娛乳，娛乳餘，汝如雨，余御汝，如魚愉，御汝餘，愈譽余。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n拉丁化後呢段抵死既野會失傳<br />\n好多詞語都有機會失傳<br />\n影響大過赤化"},{"pid":"16da29cd9b13b256d030e3097d89408cebd84630","tid":457430,"uid":68802,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T01:23:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Sor我覺得香港同台灣叫做真正正統中華文化嘅繼承<br />\n支那唔係<br />\n我地應該做嘅應該係將佢本土化而唔係將佢拉丁化<br />\n見到好多拉丁化/拼音化嘅最終只係將外來語音譯<br />\n咁不如直接講英文啦</blockquote><br />\n中國文化是優美的，只是被共產黨破壞了！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/395280?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/395280?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</blockquote><br />\n但我地唔應該好似大中華膠咁寄望支共會有改變<br />\n所以我地應該實實在在將正體中文嘅文化確確實實咁轉化成為我地合適同確切嘅香港文化<br />\n第二都唔會有包袱因爲繼承中原而要反推中原<br />\n殘體支那放棄左鐘意做食屎狗 就無資格用返正體中文"},{"pid":"2830c167797a4c55736d0cdb1afd8a788e95f589","tid":457430,"uid":86841,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T01:26:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9474ba631fca91014af46b50a741571ac0839e77","tid":457430,"uid":23385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T01:26:58.000Z","msg":"nei sick yeung cheung sick dou saw jor?"},{"pid":"0e5575f45eeb05be95894f88df9bddce9dfaf264","tid":457430,"uid":51717,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T01:27:48.000Z","msg":"要幾on 9幾自悲先諗呢個只係求割蓆效果嘅方法？"},{"pid":"ec77e733d33d0320e99d79d45b227adec92bd4b0","tid":457430,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T01:29:16.000Z","msg":"應該好似日文咁，整幾隻字母代替平時用開啲字，等班北佬睇唔撚明<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe92112147265fbf89ee50b62432c5276ace0d4c","tid":457430,"uid":139349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T01:31:39.000Z","msg":"老實講，拉丁化不如直接殘體化，筆畫簡化易學，又保留小小區別，你可以屌佢係支那文化，但係當初共產黨推廣所謂簡體都唔係冇道理，如果你畀我從越南拉丁文，韓語，殘體中文中挑選一個，我會揀殘體中文"},{"pid":"d6cda4b0576d0d26c1fb9e0f6a7bf7e95260f745","tid":457430,"uid":86841,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T01:31:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ee7c80b01b570b0397291de67be3679f5a4c41ab","tid":457430,"uid":53441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T01:32:17.000Z","msg":"咁咪好似北漏洞拉咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0eb98cd6bfba35661aacafe2e5047c4cf9214e3","tid":457430,"uid":142882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T01:33:42.000Z","msg":"越南文就拉丁化左<br />\n明明喃字先有特色"},{"pid":"53ac3960c5ed597e0de33ee750be04d8bdfeb292","tid":457430,"uid":7529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T01:34:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該好似日文咁，整幾隻字母代替平時用開啲字，等班北佬睇唔撚明<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有得諗，但唔係假名，而係諺文，比起假名更接近廣州話音節，例如韻尾方面覆蓋入聲、合口、後鼻等"},{"pid":"388071284f7d0324f763f023d0d70fc91e56c29b","tid":457430,"uid":142882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T01:34:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁咪好似北漏洞拉咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>英雄所見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aed2ba56d6cbc6cb462cc287c8971d61f82b677","tid":457430,"uid":7529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T01:36:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>應該好似日文咁，整幾隻字母代替平時用開啲字，等班北佬睇唔撚明<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有得諗，但唔係假名，而係諺文，比起假名更接近廣州話音節，例如韻尾方面覆蓋入聲、合口、後鼻等</blockquote><br />\n同埋目的唔係令「北佬」睇唔明，而係有實際作用：解決廣州話固有詞冇對應漢字問題"},{"pid":"480fc96cc68e32ffc02e95644f8c04399297f87c","tid":457430,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T01:45:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>緊持咩正體中文，不如用番草書?</blockquote><br />\n早晨<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/04/094548_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F04%2F094548_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=a23a6162&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a285cff106757e4196629df5e5ea57caeabfd7aa","tid":457430,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T01:47:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>應該好似日文咁，整幾隻字母代替平時用開啲字，等班北佬睇唔撚明<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有得諗，但唔係假名，而係諺文，比起假名更接近廣州話音節，例如韻尾方面覆蓋入聲、合口、後鼻等</blockquote><br />\n同埋目的唔係令「北佬」睇唔明，而係有實際作用：解決廣州話固有詞冇對應漢字問題</blockquote><br />\nwhy not 重新造漢字?"},{"pid":"beb333668aa593e044337a1109cf066637d54d67","tid":457430,"uid":68802,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T01:48:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>應該好似日文咁，整幾隻字母代替平時用開啲字，等班北佬睇唔撚明<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有得諗，但唔係假名，而係諺文，比起假名更接近廣州話音節，例如韻尾方面覆蓋入聲、合口、後鼻等</blockquote><br />\n同埋目的唔係令「北佬」睇唔明，而係有實際作用：解決廣州話固有詞冇對應漢字問題</blockquote><br />\n無錯<br />\n<br />\n我成日覺得咩去支化唔係咁做<br />\n支一早去正體中文化<br />\n然後霸住做中華正統個名對住我地用正體中文嘅人指手劃腳<br />\n屌你啦<br />\n我地應該要做嘅係認清事實<br />\n1.正體中文自支共放棄後已經變成只有香港台灣兩地嘅當地文化<br />\n2.香港同台灣作為正體中文唯二使用者有絕對權力去形容描述自己係咩文化<br />\n3.繼承自中原不等於中原有權力去指手劃腳 而繼承自中原亦不代表要反推中原 依個文化可以確確實實自我演化成為當地 即香港及台灣地區嘅文化而唔再同中原/支那有任何關係<br />\n基於依幾點先可以推廣出可實行嘅所謂去支化"},{"pid":"0c84de9e016b3faae335f37137e6b18e158a5534","tid":457430,"uid":33213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T01:51:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>應該好似日文咁，整幾隻字母代替平時用開啲字，等班北佬睇唔撚明<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有得諗，但唔係假名，而係諺文，比起假名更接近廣州話音節，例如韻尾方面覆蓋入聲、合口、後鼻等</blockquote><br />\n同埋目的唔係令「北佬」睇唔明，而係有實際作用：解決廣州話固有詞冇對應漢字問題</blockquote><br />\n冇字咪作新字囉<br />\n由說文解字到康熙字典到辭海<br />\n中文一直都係越來越多字<br />\n廣東話個問題係冇大家都認可嘅權威指定啲字要點寫<br />\n個個出嚟鳩噏咪亂<br />\n呢個唔係拉丁化解決到嘅問題"},{"pid":"54dfa58d00c9c77c03c4d97a711866fc2c402b2d","tid":457430,"uid":68802,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T01:51:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>應該好似日文咁，整幾隻字母代替平時用開啲字，等班北佬睇唔撚明<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有得諗，但唔係假名，而係諺文，比起假名更接近廣州話音節，例如韻尾方面覆蓋入聲、合口、後鼻等</blockquote><br />\n同埋目的唔係令「北佬」睇唔明，而係有實際作用：解決廣州話固有詞冇對應漢字問題</blockquote><br />\nwhy not 重新造漢字?</blockquote><br />\n造新字/確立常用口話有必要性<br />\n例如d嘅嗰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過依d通常要有政權/學界/巨形商業機構例如誠哥話要做<br />\n如果唔係都無可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a51b4b121725b9e98dffa2ae3ddce74c28fbde1","tid":457430,"uid":7529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T01:52:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>應該好似日文咁，整幾隻字母代替平時用開啲字，等班北佬睇唔撚明<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有得諗，但唔係假名，而係諺文，比起假名更接近廣州話音節，例如韻尾方面覆蓋入聲、合口、後鼻等</blockquote><br />\n同埋目的唔係令「北佬」睇唔明，而係有實際作用：解決廣州話固有詞冇對應漢字問題</blockquote><br />\nwhy not 重新造漢字?</blockquote><br />\n都得，我只係指出借用諺文係其中一個可行既辦法"},{"pid":"af1f915d1064b67b0156f798a269de6b25c494d2","tid":457430,"uid":68802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T01:52:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>應該好似日文咁，整幾隻字母代替平時用開啲字，等班北佬睇唔撚明<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有得諗，但唔係假名，而係諺文，比起假名更接近廣州話音節，例如韻尾方面覆蓋入聲、合口、後鼻等</blockquote><br />\n同埋目的唔係令「北佬」睇唔明，而係有實際作用：解決廣州話固有詞冇對應漢字問題</blockquote><br />\n冇字咪作新字囉<br />\n由說文解字到康熙字典到辭海<br />\n中文一直都係越來越多字<br />\n廣東話個問題係冇大家都認可嘅權威指定啲字要點寫<br />\n個個出嚟鳩噏咪亂<br />\n呢個唔係拉丁化解決到嘅問題</blockquote><br />\n無錯<br />\n無權威肯做<br />\n政府支共主理更加唔會做"},{"pid":"0e6e31954b05526f549a8e81280abac113130e61","tid":457430,"uid":60136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T01:53:55.000Z","msg":"其實無問題 呢D野整黎比外國佬/本身唔識既人學<br />\n但如果連香港人自己都要「主力」靠呢D黎學(為左清懶音 作扶助 我覺得都無問題) 就好柒囉"},{"pid":"0934e5af69ff2876cc642ec188f12a26dc4bd1ba","tid":457430,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T02:00:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>應該好似日文咁，整幾隻字母代替平時用開啲字，等班北佬睇唔撚明<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有得諗，但唔係假名，而係諺文，比起假名更接近廣州話音節，例如韻尾方面覆蓋入聲、合口、後鼻等</blockquote><br />\n同埋目的唔係令「北佬」睇唔明，而係有實際作用：解決廣州話固有詞冇對應漢字問題</blockquote><br />\nwhy not 重新造漢字?</blockquote><br />\n造新字/確立常用口話有必要性<br />\n例如d嘅嗰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過依d通常要有政權/學界/巨形商業機構例如誠哥話要做<br />\n如果唔係都無可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做新字新詞嚟取代依家啲字,到時會變到1984咁"},{"pid":"99d1b1ecd92c0e54ccb908dbfa401880950336ce","tid":457430,"uid":68802,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T02:07:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>應該好似日文咁，整幾隻字母代替平時用開啲字，等班北佬睇唔撚明<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有得諗，但唔係假名，而係諺文，比起假名更接近廣州話音節，例如韻尾方面覆蓋入聲、合口、後鼻等</blockquote><br />\n同埋目的唔係令「北佬」睇唔明，而係有實際作用：解決廣州話固有詞冇對應漢字問題</blockquote><br />\nwhy not 重新造漢字?</blockquote><br />\n造新字/確立常用口話有必要性<br />\n例如d嘅嗰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過依d通常要有政權/學界/巨形商業機構例如誠哥話要做<br />\n如果唔係都無可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做新字新詞嚟取代依家啲字,到時會變到1984咁</blockquote><br />\n由未到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加d常用口語字啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋語字文化都會演化<br />\n只要唔係硬性規定而係自然新增同去除就ok"},{"pid":"d69a0fd9b66e26fa54adc9e57c62c0cafeba9d49","tid":457430,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T02:10:24.000Z","msg":"「中文」是指「中國人」嘅文字，即是「胡語」及「殘體字」！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我們喺用「漢語」及「漢字」！"},{"pid":"6ddc39c20c5dff118d3af3d915354dc4f92f5d25","tid":457430,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T02:11:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一個音節通常對應幾個漢字，所謂拉丁化書寫只表讀音，讀者要根據context搵返對應既漢字理解，咁點解一開始唔用漢字要做多個步驟多鳩餘呢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nNei5 zan1 hai6 cyun4 bou6 zi6 sik1 daa2 gwong2 dung1 waa2?<br />\n<br />\nZau6) syun3 ni1 dou6 dou1 daai6 baa2 fo2 sing1 man6 tung1 jam1 zi6 daa2 ceot1 lai4</blockquote><br />\n有啲字「唔識」只係因為廣州話冇標準化/規範化，例如如果教育局規範「ge3」（用於連接名詞）做漢字「嘅」，香港人由小學就學呢個字，咁好多人都會「識」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSo2 ji5 o5 lin4 gwong2 dung1 waa2 gaau3 zung1 man2 dou1 faan2 deoi3<br />\n<br />\nO5 zing6 hai6 zi1 ci4 gwong2 dung1 waa2 gaau3 hau2 jyu5"},{"pid":"8a718e765b34377f2680f06bb54f716ae4e63526","tid":457430,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T02:12:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>各個國家有各個國家既國歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，呢句點變？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nNi1 geoi1 gan1 bun2 m4 hap6 gwong2 dung1 waa2 grammar"},{"pid":"324323d303942cbd1a5f377fc207107721da1fb7","tid":457430,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T02:15:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>應該好似日文咁，整幾隻字母代替平時用開啲字，等班北佬睇唔撚明<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有得諗，但唔係假名，而係諺文，比起假名更接近廣州話音節，例如韻尾方面覆蓋入聲、合口、後鼻等</blockquote><br />\n同埋目的唔係令「北佬」睇唔明，而係有實際作用：解決廣州話固有詞冇對應漢字問題</blockquote><br />\n冇字咪作新字囉<br />\n由說文解字到康熙字典到辭海<br />\n中文一直都係越來越多字<br />\n廣東話個問題係冇大家都認可嘅權威指定啲字要點寫<br />\n個個出嚟鳩噏咪亂<br />\n呢個唔係拉丁化解決到嘅問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nNei5 hai6 hoeng1 gong2 jan4 dim2 se2 dou1 ming4<br />\n<br />\nDaan6 hai6 jan4 dei6 jiu3 hok6<br />\nJau5 di1 jan4 gong2 比，畀，俾<br />\nJat1 go3 zi1 sap6 gei2 go3 se2 faat1, jan4 dei6 dim2 hok6"},{"pid":"45501ca066084c7c2eae0477a4ba1eabcad0768c","tid":457430,"uid":130339,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T02:20:07.000Z","msg":"mou5 seoi1 jiu3 wai6 zo2 jan4 dei3 tai2 dak1 ming4 ji4 fong3 hei3 zi3 gei2 gu3 jau5 se2 faat3, keoi5 jiu3 tai2 dak1 ming4 mong5 soeng6 jau5 zyun2 wun6 hei3 ho2 ji5 jung6<br />\n冇需要為咗人地睇得明已放棄自己固有寫法，佢要睇得明網上有transcriber可以轉粵拼/漢字<br />\n應該係佢就我地唔係我地就佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc147ddec250b5805890034a49d598f8e28354e0","tid":457430,"uid":51717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T02:20:45.000Z","msg":"仲on9過， 周潤&ldquo;髮&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n因為到時<br />\n法 發 髮 琺......全部變成同一個字<br />\nFaat3"},{"pid":"ce8f8d9f181a37b790dad31e7f2d69baa4127f29","tid":457430,"uid":140000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T02:28:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>應該好似日文咁，整幾隻字母代替平時用開啲字，等班北佬睇唔撚明<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有得諗，但唔係假名，而係諺文，比起假名更接近廣州話音節，例如韻尾方面覆蓋入聲、合口、後鼻等</blockquote><br />\n同埋目的唔係令「北佬」睇唔明，而係有實際作用：解決廣州話固有詞冇對應漢字問題</blockquote><br />\n冇字咪作新字囉<br />\n由說文解字到康熙字典到辭海<br />\n中文一直都係越來越多字<br />\n廣東話個問題係冇大家都認可嘅權威指定啲字要點寫<br />\n個個出嚟鳩噏咪亂<br />\n呢個唔係拉丁化解決到嘅問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nNei5 hai6 hoeng1 gong2 jan4 dim2 se2 dou1 ming4<br />\n<br />\nDaan6 hai6 jan4 dei6 jiu3 hok6<br />\nJau5 di1 jan4 gong2 比，畀，俾<br />\nJat1 go3 zi1 sap6 gei2 go3 se2 faat1, jan4 dei6 dim2 hok6</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n反而我覺得睇樓主你咁樣寫會仲難明<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有啲詞語如果響冇得用上文下例推論嘅時候就咁用拼音好易出事<br />\n例如我寫:<br />\nngo5 heoi3 maai5 coeng1<br />\n咁我係寫緊槍定窗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身粵語響講嘅時候都已經會因為同音而要問清楚<br />\n而問嘅方法好多時係問你點樣寫<br />\n例如上面咁我可以話木字邊嗰個coeng1字<br />\n但係取代咗漢字咁只會令到用嘅時候出現麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"888bff6ae2b650e2233338b9f5801c11484dfd74","tid":457430,"uid":51717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T02:45:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>應該好似日文咁，整幾隻字母代替平時用開啲字，等班北佬睇唔撚明<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有得諗，但唔係假名，而係諺文，比起假名更接近廣州話音節，例如韻尾方面覆蓋入聲、合口、後鼻等</blockquote><br />\n同埋目的唔係令「北佬」睇唔明，而係有實際作用：解決廣州話固有詞冇對應漢字問題</blockquote><br />\n冇字咪作新字囉<br />\n由說文解字到康熙字典到辭海<br />\n中文一直都係越來越多字<br />\n廣東話個問題係冇大家都認可嘅權威指定啲字要點寫<br />\n個個出嚟鳩噏咪亂<br />\n呢個唔係拉丁化解決到嘅問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nNei5 hai6 hoeng1 gong2 jan4 dim2 se2 dou1 ming4<br />\n<br />\nDaan6 hai6 jan4 dei6 jiu3 hok6<br />\nJau5 di1 jan4 gong2 比，畀，俾<br />\nJat1 go3 zi1 sap6 gei2 go3 se2 faat1, jan4 dei6 dim2 hok6</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n反而我覺得睇樓主你咁樣寫會仲難明<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有啲詞語如果響冇得用上文下例推論嘅時候就咁用拼音好易出事<br />\n例如我寫:<br />\nngo5 heoi3 maai5 coeng1<br />\n咁我係寫緊槍定窗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身粵語響講嘅時候都已經會因為同音而要問清楚<br />\n而問嘅方法好多時係問你點樣寫<br />\n例如上面咁我可以話木字邊嗰個coeng1字<br />\n但係取代咗漢字咁只會令到用嘅時候出現麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲有，拉丁語系係拼音文字，講嘅時侯兩個就算音一樣，但書寫拼法唔同(hole whole)<br />\n但將中文拉丁化，捨棄本身文字，咁講同音寫又同字，跟本就無辦法有效溝通同分辨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n司 絲 獅 師 思 撕 斯 俬 詩 施 私屍 尸 <br />\n拉打化之後呢堆常用字得返一個字<br />\nsi1 <br />\n何其簡陋。。。<br />\n最徹底嘅滅粤方法"},{"pid":"097f2093af1ca98f0997159b0dcb381405e6b1b6","tid":457430,"uid":35730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T02:46:55.000Z","msg":"d拼音一句都睇唔明，家下姐係方便鬼佬杯舊香港人姐"},{"pid":"4bd1b33217a613a2bcf4eadb5af43d439f4ed85b","tid":457430,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T02:49:13.000Z","msg":"普通話拼音較容易<br />\n廣東話拼音太複雜"},{"pid":"2134994ec4c375aae977e25a206ef5983b407e83","tid":457430,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T02:50:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一個音節通常對應幾個漢字，所謂拉丁化書寫只表讀音，讀者要根據context搵返對應既漢字理解，咁點解一開始唔用漢字要做多個步驟多鳩餘呢？</blockquote><br />\n因為唔洗再學漢字，小學雞以後唔洗抄詞語"},{"pid":"1d9821b682bb0c343ae0e1cf3163e88a4864208e","tid":457430,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T03:03:29.000Z","msg":"on撚鳩，仲撚柒過共匪推殘體字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"240b2f3335d67153ffc885b24dd7bd874fbb049b","tid":457430,"uid":48670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T03:05:55.000Z","msg":"會搞到同韓文一樣 <br />\n棄漢字用諺文<br />\n結果要玩估字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe275ec82ad7163de30614bee49c20734fe8537c","tid":457430,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T03:06:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>on撚鳩，仲撚柒過共匪推殘體字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最徹底摧毀廣東話同正體字既方法"},{"pid":"721769085f9350f5e5e9915b96ff5e52c411057d","tid":457430,"uid":49588,"like"